title: Tin Foil Hat Ep 7: Will The Real Paul McCartney Please Stand Up
description:
Thank you for tuning into another episode of Tin Foil Hat. This episode I welcome Those Conspiracy Guys' Gordon Rochford and we discuss...
1) Donald Trump
2) The Deep State
*** I know you guys like it when we talk about one thing but a bombshell just dropped right before the podcast.*******
3) Did Paul McCartney die and get replace by a look alike?
